                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-318" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM TYLER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. Bass. I took the prisoner, and this jacket of mine and these other things dropped from him—I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183708140045"></xptr>
               <p>had seen this jacket safe in my master's shop an hour before, and the scales and weights I saw an hour and a half before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I picked them up and was going to tee if I could find an owner for them.</p>
